<div class="col-md-12">
    <div class="row box">
        <div class="box-inner col-md-6 ">
            <h1 class="title">Cats Homeland</h1>
            <p class="slogan">Cats Homeland专门收养流浪猫，
                <br>
                我们提供暂住所，
                并用我们的力量为猫猫找到新主人。
                <br>
                通过这里，你找到一个它。
                <br>
                快来提交申请，给它一个温暖的家。
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
                <%= link_to '来领它吧', jobs_path, class: 'btn btn-danger' %>
                <%= link_to '帮它找主人吧', admin_jobs_path, class: 'btn btn-info' %>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="content-section-a">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-6">
                <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                <div class="clearfix"></div>
                <h1 class="section-heading">爱猫人士拍的一个视频</h1>
                <p class="lead">有网友以流浪猫的视角拍摄了一段视频分享给你们</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-0 col-sm-6">
                <%= video_tag "cat.mp4", loop: :loop, mute: :mute, :controls => true, class: "video" %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-section-b">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1 col-sm-push-6  col-sm-6">
                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h2 class="section-heading">小猫送出前保证健康</h2>
                    <p class="lead">请收到小猫后，再去宠物医院做一次检查哦！</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-pull-6  col-sm-6">
                    <%= image_tag 'cat1.jpeg', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-section-a">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-6">
                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h2 class="section-heading">我们提供太空舱送猫猫安全到新家
                        <h2>
                            <p class="lead">如果你不会养猫，就一定要多上网寻求帮助，例如<a target="_blank" href="http://ailinjuly-blog.logdown.com">Ailin 的 Blog</a>! 啦啦啦啦啦啦啦</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-2 col-sm-6">
                            <%= image_tag 'cathouse.jpg', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!--开始slide-->
            <!-- Add this css File in head tag-->
            <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" media="all">
            <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.5.2/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet" media="all">
            <!--
                   If you want to change #bootstrap-touch-slider id then you have to change Carousel-indicators and Carousel-Control  #bootstrap-touch-slider slide as well
                   Slide effect: slide, fade
                   Text Align: slide_style_center, slide_style_left, slide_style_right
                   Add Text Animation: https://daneden.github.io/animate.css/
                   -->
            <div id="bootstrap-touch-slider" class="carousel bs-slider slide  control-round indicators-line" data-ride="carousel" data-pause="hover" data-interval="5000" >
                <!-- Indicators -->
                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#bootstrap-touch-slider" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#bootstrap-touch-slider" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                    <li data-target="#bootstrap-touch-slider" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                </ol>
                <!-- Wrapper For Slides -->
                <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                    <!-- Third Slide -->
                    <div class="item active">
                        <!-- Slide Background -->
                        <img src="https://static.pexels.com/photos/45170/kittens-cat-cat-puppy-rush-45170.jpeg" alt="Bootstrap Touch Slider"  class="slide-image"/>
                        <div class="bs-slider-overlay"></div>
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                <!-- Slide Text Layer -->
                                <div class="slide-text slide_style_left">
                                    <h1 data-animation="animated zoomInRight">我们童年时养过的那些猫咪</h1>
                                    <p data-animation="animated fadeInLeft">小时候，养过两只猫，一只被妈妈送走了，一只自己跳到鱼缸中淹死了。
                                        <br>
                                        至今还记得6岁的我爬到床底下帮猫猫擦💩的事情......</p>
                                    <a href="http://bootstrapthemes.co/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default" data-animation="animated fadeInLeft">select one</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- End of Slide -->
                    <!-- Second Slide -->
                    <div class="item">
                        <!-- Slide Background -->
                        <img src="https://static.pexels.com/photos/26897/pexels-photo-26897.jpg" alt="Bootstrap Touch Slider"  class="slide-image"/>
                        <div class="bs-slider-overlay"></div>
                        <!-- Slide Text Layer -->
                        <div class="slide-text slide_style_center">
                            <h2 data-animation="animated zoomInRight">She says：</h2>
                            <p data-animation="animated lightSpeedIn">While cats love to be near you, they are also cool about giving you space when they know that you need it.
                                <br>
                                Cats are loving, have the ability to read our emotions, and make us feel special with their desire to be near us whenever we are around.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- End of Slide -->
                    <!-- Third Slide -->
                    <div class="item">
                        <!-- Slide Background -->
                        <img src="https://static.pexels.com/photos/202737/pexels-photo-202737.jpeg" alt="Bootstrap Touch Slider"  class="slide-image"/>
                        <div class="bs-slider-overlay"></div>
                        <!-- Slide Text Layer -->
                        <div class="slide-text slide_style_right">
                            <h1 data-animation="animated zoomInLeft">服务介绍</h1>
                            <p data-animation="animated fadeInRight">我们的猫咪都是好心人捡到送来的，也有旧主人送来的.
                                <br>
                                您可以提交领养申请，描述你要的猫猫种类和上传一张猫猫照片。我们会第一时间联系您！</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- End of Slide -->
                </div>
                <!-- End of Wrapper For Slides -->
                <!-- Left Control -->
                <a class="left carousel-control" href="#bootstrap-touch-slider" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="fa fa-angle-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <!-- Right Control -->
                <a class="right carousel-control" href="#bootstrap-touch-slider" role="button" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="fa fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
